	<TextAndImageHero reversed>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>Welcome!</h1>
			<p>I'm DonvitoCodes, I livestream about Tech & Startups in Twitch. Welcome to my website where you can get updated with what is latest.</p>
		</div>
		<div slot="btns-container">
			<Button href="https://twitch.tv/donvitocodes" customIcon>Follow me in Twitch!
